the colour of the black cherry and purple grape may be known
by their autumnal tints; and that even in plants, which have
&s;prung from &s;eed in the preceding &s;pring; as the tinging matter
in the leaves of the&s;e plants is probably of the &s;ame kind as that,
to which the fruits will in future owe their colour.&endq; The
leaves of the purple grape become quite red in autumn, as well
