<P><HI>The &s;tar-clad Virgin,</HI> 22d of Augu&s;t. <HI>Golden &s;cales,</HI> 22d of September.</P>
<P><HI>Scorpion,</HI> 22d of October. <HI>Evade the fro&s;t.</HI> One advantage, which ve|getables
